WEBVTT

00:07:29.958 --> 00:07:32.948
such that you have to use
a stool to reach it,

00:07:32.972 --> 00:07:35.266
even when it's chocolate,

00:07:35.290 --> 00:07:41.004
study participants ate 70 percent less
without thinking about it.

00:07:41.028 --> 00:07:42.178
I know.

00:07:42.202 --> 00:07:43.688
Let that sit for a second.

00:07:43.712 --> 00:07:45.252
(Laughter)

00:07:45.276 --> 00:07:50.193
Design to make the choices
you wish to make easier.

00:07:50.495 --> 00:07:54.574
Which bring us to the third step
to go from Crazy Mode to Ready Mode,

00:07:54.598 --> 00:07:57.965
and that is to get out of your head.

00:07:58.455 --> 00:07:59.621
Come with me.

00:07:59.645 --> 00:08:00.795
Different story.